l\" role=\"button\" tabindex=\"0\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-feedback\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-feedback\"></use></svg><span class=\"zDocsFeedbackButtonText\"> Feedback</span></span></div></div><div class=\"zDocsTopicActionsMobile\"><button aria-label=\"Show topic actions\" data-toggle=\"dropdown\" id=\"zDocsTopicActionsMobile\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-ellipsis-h\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-ellipsis-h\"></use></svg></button><div class=\"dropdown-menu zDocsDropdownMenu zDocsTopicActionsMobileDropdown dropdown-menu-right\"></div></div><div style=\"flex-basis: 100%; height: 0px;\"></div><ul class=\"zDocsTopicPageDetails\"><li class=\"zDocsTopicPageDate css-cinqea\">Last Updated<span class=\"css-cinqea\">Okt 10, 2024</span></li><li class=\"zDocsAiTopicSummaryDetailsItem\"><button class=\"zDocsAiTopicSummaryButton\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-topic-summary\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-topic-summary\"></use></svg>Summarize</button></li><li class=\"spacer\" role=\"presentation\"></li><div class=\"zDocsLabelWrapper\"><ul><li class=\"zDocsLabel\"><a aria-describedby=\"hyperLinkFacetsTooltip\" class=\"css-ettsdk\" data-tooltip-content=\"Search all site by tag: Uniface\" data-tooltip-id=\"hyperLinkFacetsTooltip\" href=\"/de-DE/search?labelkey=prod_uniface\" stylesprops=\"[object Object]\"><svg aria-label=\"Tag\" class=\"ico-tag\" role=\"img\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-tag\"></use></svg>Uniface</a></li><li class=\"zDocsLabel\"><a aria-describedby=\"hyperLinkFacetsTooltip\" class=\"css-ettsdk\" data-tooltip-content=\"Search all site by tag: 10.4\" data-tooltip-id=\"hyperLinkFacetsTooltip\" href=\"/de-DE/search?labelkey=uniface_10.4\" stylesprops=\"[object Object]\"><svg aria-label=\"Tag\" class=\"ico-tag\" role=\"img\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-tag\"></use></svg>10.4</a></li></ul></div></ul></header><div class=\"zDocsTopicPageBody\" data-prismjs-copy=\"Copy\" data-prismjs-copy-error=\"Copy failed! Use Ctrl + C instead.\" data-prismjs-copy-success=\"Copied!\"><div class=\"zDocsTopicPageBodyContent wide\" dir=\"ltr\"><div id=\"zDocsAiSummaryContaineruniface_104vlc1665703063465.html\"></div><div><article class=\"hascomments\" data-page=\"bundle:uniface_104/enus/vlc1665703063465.html\" id=\"bundle:uniface_104/enus/vlc1665703063465.html\"><main role=\"main\"><article aria-labelledby=\"ariaid-title1\" class=\"dita\" id=\"vlc1665703063465\" role=\"article\">\n<h1 class=\"title topictitle1\" id=\"ariaid-title1\">\n      html:type\n </h1>\n<div class=\"body conbody\"><p class=\"shortdesc\">DSP widget property that sets the <code class=\"ph codeph\">type</code> attribute of the HTML <code class=\"ph codeph\">input</code> element that is bound to the widget. Any type supported by the HTML standard is allowed. If a browser does not support a given type, the <code class=\"ph codeph\">text</code> type is used.\n </p>\n<section class=\"section refsyn\" id=\"vlc1665703063465__topic_d101276e1_d101277e1_d101278e1\">\n<p class=\"p\" id=\"vlc1665703063465__p_d101279e1_d101280e1_d101281e1\">html:type\n                                 <code class=\"ph codeph\">=</code>\n<var class=\"keyword varname\">HtmlControlType</var>\n</p>\n</section>\n<section class=\"section p\" id=\"vlc1665703063465__section_w5383ab1b5b3_w5384ab1b5_w5385ab1\">\n<p class=\"p\" id=\"vlc1665703063465__p_d101282e1_d101283e1_d101284e1\">Example: <code class=\"ph codeph\">\"html:type=date\"</code>\n</p>\n</section>\n<section class=\"section\" id=\"vlc1665703063465__section_wzr_yz4_5wb\"><h2 class=\"title sectiontitle\" id=\"d93276e81\">Values</h2>\n<p class=\"p\" id=\"vlc1665703063465__p_d101288e1_d101289e1_d101290e1\">\n<var class=\"keyword varname\">HtmlControlType</var>—valid value for the <code class=\"ph codeph\">type</code> attribute of\n        the HTML <code class=\"ph codeph\">input</code> element. Valid values include:</p>\n<ul class=\"ul\" id=\"vlc1665703063465__ul_ayr_zz4_5wb\">\n<li class=\"li\" id=\"vlc1665703063465__li_d41042e1_d41043e1_d41044e1\">button </li>\n<li class=\"li\" id=\"vlc1665703063465__li_d41045e1_d41046e1_d41047e1\">checkbox </li>\n<li class=\"li\" id=\"vlc1665703063465__li_d41048e1_d41049e1_d41050e1\">color </li>\n<li class=\"li\" id=\"vlc1665703063465__li_d41051e1_d41052e1_d41053e1\">date </li>\n<li class=\"li\" id=\"vlc1665703063465__li_d41054e1_d41055e1_d41056e1\">datetime </li>\n<li class=\"li\" id=\"vlc1665703063465__li_d41057e1_d41058e1_d41059e1\">datetime-local </li>\n<li class=\"li\" id=\"vlc1665703063465__li_d41060e1_d41061e1_d41062e1\">email </li>\n<li class=\"li\" id=\"vlc1665703063465__li_d41063e1_d41064e1_d41065e1\">hidden </li>\n<li class=\"li\" id=\"vlc1665703063465__li_d41066e1_d41067e1_d41068e1\">month </li>\n<li class=\"li\" id=\"vlc1665703063465__li_d41069e1_d41070e1_d41071e1\">number </li>\n<li class=\"li\" id=\"vlc1665703063465__li_d41072e1_d41073e1_d41074e1\">password </li>\n<li class=\"li\" id=\"vlc1665703063465__li_d41075e1_d41076e1_d41077e1\">range </li>\n<li class=\"li\" id=\"vlc1665703063465__li_d41078e1_d41079e1_d41080e1\">search </li>\n<li class=\"li\" id=\"vlc1665703063465__li_d41081e1_d41082e1_d41083e1\">tel </li>\n<li class=\"li\" id=\"vlc1665703063465__li_d41084e1_d41085e1_d41086e1\">text </li>\n<li class=\"li\" id=\"vlc1665703063465__li_d41087e1_d41088e1_d41089e1\">time </li>\n<li class=\"li\" id=\"vlc1665703063465__li_d41090e1_d41091e1_d41092e1\">url </li>\n<li class=\"li\" id=\"vlc1665703063465__li_d41093e1_d41094e1_d41095e1\">week </li>\n</ul>\n<p class=\"p\" id=\"vlc1665703063465__p_d101291e1_d101292e1_d101293e1\">For more information, refer to HTML reference\n        information available on the web, such as that provided by MDN: <a class=\"xref\" href=\"https://developer.mozilla.org/en-US/docs/Web/HTML/Element/input\" rel=\"external noopener\" target=\"_blank\">input</a>.</p>\n</section>\n<section class=\"section\" id=\"vlc1665703063465__section_etd_p1p_5wb\"><h2 class=\"title sectiontitle\" id=\"d93276e166\">Usage</h2>\n<div class=\"table-wrap\"><table class=\"table\" count-columns=\"2\" id=\"vlc1665703063465__table_d11909e1_d11910e1_d11911e1\"><caption></caption><colgroup><col/><col/></colgroup><tbody class=\"tbody\">\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<p class=\"p\">Dynamic?</p>\n</td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<p class=\"p\">Yes</p>\n</td>\n</tr>\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<p class=\"p\">Dependencies:</p>\n</td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<p class=\"p\">Supported types depend on the browser</p>\n</td>\n</tr>\n</tbody></table></div>\n</section>\n<section class=\"section\" id=\"vlc1665703063465__section_un4_q1p_5wb\"><h2 class=\"title sectiontitle\" id=\"d93276e215\">Description</h2>\n<p class=\"p\" id=\"vlc1665703063465__p_d101300e1_d101301e1_d101302e1\">The html:type property determines the HTML control\n        used to represent that data. For more information, see <a class=\"xref\" data-bundleid=\"uniface_104\" data-navpath=\"sno1665702583691.html\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/sno1665702583691.html\" title=\"Widget definitions for Dynamic Server Pages (DSPs) are used to generate the HTML elements and controls used to represent fields, labels, occurrences, and entities displayed in the client browser.\">Widgets for Dynamic Server Pages</a>.</p>\n</section>\n<section class=\"section\" id=\"vlc1665703063465__section_gnd_s1p_5wb\"><h2 class=\"title sectiontitle\" id=\"d93276e232\">Applies To</h2>\n<ul class=\"ul\" id=\"vlc1665703063465__ul_ufn_t1p_5wb\">\n<li class=\"li\" id=\"vlc1665703063465__li_d41096e1_d41097e1_d41098e1\">All DSP widgets </li>\n</ul>\n</section>\n</div>\n</article></main></article>\n</div></div></div><div class=\"bottomFeedback\"><div aria-labelledby=\"bottomFeedbackText\" class=\"bottomFeedbackContent\" role=\"group\"><span class=\"bottomFeedbackText\" id=\"bottomFeedbackText\">Was this topic helpful?</span><div class=\"bottomFeedbackButtonGroup\"><a data-backdrop=\"static\" data-target=\"#feedbackModal_bottom_3616534\" data-toggle=\"modal\" href=\"#\" role=\"button\" type=\"button\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-thumbs-up\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-thumbs-up\"></use></svg><span>Like</span></a><a data-backdrop=\"static\" data-target=\"#feedbackModal_bottom_3616534\" data-toggle=\"modal\" href=\"#\" role=\"button\" type=\"button\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-thumbs-down\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-thumbs-down\"></use></svg><span>Dislike</span></a></div></div></div><div style=\"position: fixed; bottom: 170px; right: 70px; cursor: pointer; transition-duration: 0.2s; transition-timing-function: linear; transition-delay: 0s; z-index: 3; opacity: 0; visibility: hidden; transition-property: opacity, visibility;\"><button aria-label=\"Scroll to top\" class=\"zDocsScrollTopBtn\" data-tooltip-content=\"Scroll to top\" data-tooltip-id=\"zDocsBackToTopToolTip\" id=\"zDocsScrollToTop\" type=\"button\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-next\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-next\"></use></svg></button></div></body></html>", "text": "html:type Add to My Topics Add selected topic and subtopics Add Topic & Subtopics with topic head Add entire publication Watch Download PDF Save selected topic Save selected topic and subtopics Save entire publication Share Email Link Copy Link Feedback Last Updated Okt 10, 2024 Summarize Uniface 10.4 html:type DSP widget property that sets the type attribute of the HTML input element that is bound to the widget. Any type supported by the HTML standard is allowed. If a browser does not support a given type, the text type is used. html:type = HtmlControlType Example: \"html:type=date\" Values HtmlControlType —valid value for the type attribute of the HTML input element. Valid values include: button checkbox color date datetime datetime-local email hidden month number password range search tel text time url week For more information, refer to HTML reference information available on the web, such as that provided by MDN: input . Usage Dynamic? Yes Dependencies: Supported types depend on the browser Description The html:type property determines the HTML control used to represent that data. For more information, see Widgets for Dynamic Server Pages . Applies To All DSP widgets Was this topic helpful? Like Dislike"}